text:
Available state fuel sites for Essential Healthcare Workers. When healthcare workers arrive at one of the following stations, must present their work badges, as these four locations are only for essential healthcare workers.
-Pinellas County
- 2985 Drew Street Clearwater (BayCare corporate office parking lot)
- 7300 Bryan Dairy Rd Largo (Tampa Bay Health Care Coalition-this site is open 24 hours)
- 801 Sith Avenue S. St. Petersburg (Johns Hopkins All Children)
Hillsborough County
- 4600 Habana Avenue Tampa (In large parking area north)
Other Fuel Sites
trans:
